      "paragraphs": [
        "Tuple type for `change()`'s single options parameter: present-and-required whenever `ChangeSceneOptions<Data>` has a required `data` field (`Data` is not `void`), optional otherwise. There is no runtime data/options ambiguity to resolve anymore — `data` always lives inside this one object, never as a separate positional argument (spec §6.3; this supersedes the deleted two-argument `SetSceneArgs`)."
      ],
